        <note>Commentary colophon: iti śrīmatparamahaṃsaparivrājakāyacārya śrībhāratītīrthavidyāraṇyamunivaryakiṃkareṇa rāmakṛṣṇakhyaviduṣāviracitā dvaitavivekapadavyākhyā samāptā // (f. 9v).</note>
